definition: to cover/to wrap/to hold/to include/to take charge of/to contract (to or for)/package/wrapper/container/bag/to hold or embrace/bundle/packet/CL:個|个[ge4],隻|只[zhi1]

sentences.english: Here is a list of what it will include.
sentences.chinese: 以下是它所能够包含的新特性列表。

sentences.english: Some of Pedini collections includes nice re-invent of inline kitchen layouts.
sentences.chinese: 一些佩蒂尼的产品包含了重新发明的内嵌厨具布局。

sentences.english: Implementing customer scenarios to include the flow of defect submissions expands integration coverage.
sentences.chinese: 包含缺陷交付流程的实施客户场景扩展了集成的范围。

sentences.english: Meshes with vertex colors, normals and one or two UV sets.
sentences.chinese: 网格模型包含顶点颜色，法线，一到两个uv集。

sentences.english: Two special units focusing on initial and final consonant clusters.
sentences.chinese: 包含两个特别的单元，提供字首与字尾子音群的练习。

sentences.english: Each file contains linear PCM essence.
sentences.chinese: 每个文件都包含有线性PCM精髓。

sentences.english: You can specify which non-key columns to include in the index and use the arrows again to specify the order.
sentences.chinese: 可以指定索引中包含哪些非键列并用箭头指定次序。

sentences.english: Make the directory containing the files the current working directory.
sentences.chinese: 将包含这些文件的目录作为当前工作目录。

sentences.english: This requirement will gradually expand to include smaller public companies in the future.
sentences.chinese: 这一要求将在未来逐步扩展到包含更小的国有公司。

sentences.english: This result was also confirmed by neomycin gene-containing replicons with same mutations.
sentences.chinese: 这一结果在新霉素包含子转染中也得到了证实。

sentences.english: Contains settings to manage Remote Procedure Call troubleshooting .
sentences.chinese: 包含管理远程过程调用疑难解答的设置。

sentences.english: Run time and designer licenses are included in all three editions.
sentences.chinese: 这三个版本中都包含运行时和设计者许可证。

sentences.english: For example, the charting widget has a tests directory that contains code to get you started.
sentences.chinese: 例如，图表小部件的测试目录包含入门代码。

sentences.english: Lie all the Verities and Realities of your Existence;
sentences.chinese: 包含着你生活中所有最真实的方面。

sentences.english: This volume contains selections from his early works.
sentences.chinese: 该卷包含了他的早期作品文选。

sentences.english: Marx and Engels's system of division of labour is multileveled.
sentences.chinese: 马恩著作中的分工是一个包含多层次的分工体系。
